com.siperian.sif.message.mrm

Class GetSystemTrustSettingsResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.siperian.sif.message.SiperianResponse
      • com.siperian.sif.message.mrm.GetSystemTrustSettingsResponse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class GetSystemTrustSettingsResponse
extends SiperianResponse
    Response to a GetSystemTrustSettingsRequest.

    The response contains one trust setting object for each column UID specified in the request, in the same order as the list of column UIDs in the request.

    Usage Example:

    The following example shows how to print out the system trust settings in a GetSystemTrustSettingsResponse:

    GetSystemTrustSettingsResponse response =
    (GetSystemTrustSettingsResponse) sipClient.process(request);
    ArrayList trustSettingsList = response.getTrustSettings();
    for(int i=0; i < trustSettingsList.size(); i++)
    {
      TrustSetting trustSetting = (TrustSetting) trustSettingsList.get(i);
      System.out.println("Trust settings for column "+i+":");
      System.out.println(" Summary: trust decays from "+trustSetting.getMaximumTrust()
        + " to " + trustSetting.getMinimumTrust()
        + " in " + trustSetting.getMaximumTimeUnits() + " " + trustSetting.getTimeUnit() + "(s)"
        + " in a " + trustSetting.getGraphType() + " manner.");
      System.out.println(" Maximum Trust: "+trustSetting.getMaximumTrust());
      System.out.println(" Minimum Trust: "+trustSetting.getMinimumTrust());
      System.out.println(" Decay Graph Type: "+trustSetting.getGraphType());
      System.out.println(" Maximum Time Units: "+trustSetting.getMaximumTimeUnits());
      System.out.println(" Time Units: "+trustSetting.getTimeUnit());
      System.out.println(" Is Custom: "+trustSetting.isCustom());
      System.out.println(" Encoded format: "+trustSetting.getAsEncodedString());
    }

    For more details, see GetSystemTrustSettingsRequest.

    See Also:
    GetSystemTrustSettingsRequest, TrustSetting, Serialized Form

    API Pair: GetSystemTrustSettingsRequest

    API Group: Data Steward
